snippet.title: Chop Chop Guys - First Playable Prototype Trailer
snippet.description:
Chop Chop Guys is a wild competition game of dim-witted characters racing through a world of zany traps. The prototype is available for a playtest on Steam now.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2008220/Chop_Chop_Guys/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=fpptrailer291222
